data.description: Great house for a handyman or investor. Come see this open floor plan living room, family room, dining room and kitchen great for entertaining. Also has full bathroom on first floor. Rear sliding doors lead to a deck and fenced in backyard. Upstairs has 4 generous size bedrooms with 2 full baths. 2 zone AC with forced hot air heat. Great location at the end of the street. All this house needs is some attention but has great potential.
